are markedly different from those of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Hendel" authorityYear="1923" box="[767,913,284,308]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Fagaceae" genus="Quercus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Fagales" pageId="13" pageNumber="312" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="pubescens">
